WEBVTT

00:10.343 --> 00:11.343
What the fuck?

00:11.386 --> 00:12.905
<i>I'm telling you, it was crazy.</i>

00:12.929 --> 00:14.865
<i>We knock, you know,
to make sure no one's left in the house.</i>

00:14.889 --> 00:17.529
I'm thinking maybe he lives
with his mother or something like that.

00:17.559 --> 00:21.062
And who opens the door
but Chris McCarthy himself.

00:21.146 --> 00:21.980
What did you do?

00:22.063 --> 00:23.903
You should've seen her, Duvall,
balls of steel.

00:23.940 --> 00:25.459
Had a cover story right there
in her back pocket.

00:25.483 --> 00:27.563
Well, ten years undercover,
you learn to be prepared.

00:27.610 --> 00:30.864
So, who was I following,
and whose DNA are we holding here?

00:30.947 --> 00:33.575
<i>Curtis McCarthy,
Chris McCarthy's brother.</i>

00:33.658 --> 00:34.784
<i>They live together.</i>

00:37.078 --> 00:39.205
Take that mug over to CBI
and request a rush.

00:39.289 --> 00:41.624
Tell them to call my cell the second
they get the results,

00:41.708 --> 00:43.626
I don't care what time it is.
So, we get a guy

00:43.710 --> 00:46.337
who meets the same physical description,
same address,

00:46.421 --> 00:47.964
so access to the same vehicle...

00:48.048 --> 00:51.259
Yeah, we just went from having
one suspect to having two.

